@startuml
title CI Test Import Graph (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #F7FFF8
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Courier

actor "GitHub Actions\n(npm test)" as gha #E6F3FF
rectangle "Repo Root\nnode_modules" as rootMods #E8F5E9
rectangle "Root Test\nreact-test-sdk-hooks-integration.test.ts" as rootTest #FFF2CC
rectangle "Test SDK Server\ntest-sdk/src/server.ts" as sdkServer #E1F5FE
component "express package" as expressPkg #C8E6C9

gha --> rootTest : run Node test runner
rootTest --> sdkServer : import createAthenaTestSdkServer()
sdkServer --> expressPkg : import express
expressPkg --> rootMods : resolved from root devDependencies

note right of rootMods
Root package.json now declares express in devDependencies.
Clean CI install provides express for root test imports.
end note

note bottom of rootTest #C5E1A5
react-test-sdk-hooks-integration.test.ts runs without module resolution failure
end note
@enduml
